<br>
It is a stark and grim reminder to us all about the finiteness and preciousness of Life.<br>
<br>
Too often, whether in a MMORPG or in the hustle &amp; bustle of real-life, people often lose sight of the delicate nature of our existences.<br>
<br>
Perhaps that explains, at least in part, why some people find it so easy to use &amp; abuse their fellow humans in a desperate (and, ultimately, meaningless) attempt at self-aggrandizement.<br>
<br>
The loss of one of us diminishes us all, and the winking-out of a gentle spirit and light like &quot;Opaal&quot; makes our universe a smaller, darker, and colder place.<br>
<br>
My deepest condolences go to the family and friends who had the honour and privilege of knowing her well and loving her dearly.<br>
<br>
TAL <br>
